description: Reserved matters application seeking approval of appearance, landscaping, layout and scale for Phase 2 of Mill Hill East development pursuant to Condition 5 of Outline planning permission reference H/04017/09 dated: 22/9/2011 involving the erection of 103 dwellings comprising 3 x one bed flats, 20 x two bed flats, 45 x 3 bed houses, 25 x four bed houses and 10 x five bed houses. Approval of layout and landscaping works to Phase 2 public open space (OS2), together with details to discharge the requirements of:  Conditions 12 (relating to Plot L only); 57 (relating to plots within Phase 2 only); and 8,26, 27, 29, 48, 52, 70, 80, 83, 85 and 91 all in relation to Phase 2 only.
